data.description: Look no further! Updated 2-bed, 2-bath CBS home on a secure 1.15-acre lot. This residence boasts an open floor plan, with a modern kitchen, stainless steel appliances, and a generously sized kitchen island.  Noteworthy features include a 2015 roof, a 2019 water pump & heater, and accordion storm shutters. Step onto the front porch to behold your private pond, surrounded by picturesque bamboo trees. An extra entertainment building, complete with a carport, water/electricity, updated salt filtration system, patio, and fruitful trees, elevates the charm. The expansive lot invites potential additions, be it home extensions, outdoor havens, or a new pool. Offering the best value in the area, this property welcomes creative enhancements and has plenty of potential and upside!
